<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_38" id="18v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_38_r2l1">Holfelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l4"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Als Jr vns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / vvie Jr einen
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l5"><expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan> genant Heincʒ
                                <expan>Pütn<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vanknüʒʒ gehabt
                            hat </del> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l6">gehabt habt in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> venknüʒʒ /
                        der ew daraws <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l7">ſeÿ vvorden / vnd man beſchuldig ew / daʒ Jr vns
                        botſchaft </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l8">getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſüllet / daʒ vvir
                        die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒü ew gen Holfelt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l9">ſchıcken <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / ſo woltet Jr
                        vns <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mıtburg<ex>er</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l10"><expan>antwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . Darauf ir begert
                        / daʒ vvir ew des <expan>entſchuldige<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l13">ſüllen / . Nu wiſſen <add><ab facs="#facs_38_line_1576491013322_7874">wir da </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> wir </del> von <del rend="strikethrough"> der
                            ſache </del> nichts / vnd Jr habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l14">vns auch kein botſchaft von des
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ewrs
                            <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l15">getan / vnd wöllen ew des
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> entſchuldigen / vnd wo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l16">vvir des rede <expan>hört<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>verantwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / wan Jr des vnſchuldig </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_38_r2l18">ſeit / <del rend="strikethrough">vnd vvo w </del> /
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Luce
                                <expan>ew<ex>a</ex>n<ex>gelis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan> .
                    </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_38" id="18v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Holfelt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, wie ir einen
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan>, genant Heincz
                            <expan>Pütn<ex>er</ex></expan>, gehabt habt in
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> venknüzz, der ew daraws
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey worden; und man beschuldig ew,
                        daz ir uns botschaft getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> süllet, daz wir die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czü ew gen Holfelt schicken
                                <expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so woltet ir uns
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>antwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Darauf ir begert, daz wir ew des
                                <expan>entschuldige<ex>n</ex></expan> süllen. Nu wissen <add>wir
                            da</add> von nichts und ir habt uns auch kein botschaft von des
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ewrs
                            <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> getan und wöllen ew des
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> entschuldigen und, wo wir des rede
                                <expan>hört<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        <expan>verantwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wan ir des unschuldig seit.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                            <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Luce
                                <expan>ew<ex>a</ex>n<ex>gelis</ex><hi rend="sup">te</hi></expan>.
                    </ab>
</div>
